Horror							KEY:Horror ~ Nightmare Constructor			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																		DEFINE:HorrorLVL|0												DESC:You are able to form a creature created from distilled fears and nightmares.  Creating a horror takes one minute of concentration to complete and the horror remains until dismissed by you.  This horror functions as a summoner's eidolon using your class level as the summoner level, with the following exceptions.  A horror is a mindless construct like an astral construct and not an outsider, so it is subject to effects like dismiss ectoplasm instead of effects like banishment.  Commanding a horror is the same as commanding an astral construct.  A horror disperses if you are rendered unconscious or die.  You can allow your horror to use your terrors, but such uses still count against your daily limit.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			BONUS:VAR|HorrorLVL|DreadLVL											FOLLOWERS:Horror|1	COMPANIONLIST:Horror|Horror (Biped),Horror (Quadruped),Horror (Serpentine)			SOURCEPAGE:p.268
Devastating Touch						KEY:Devastating Touch ~ Nightmare Constructor	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																	DESC:Your horror gains the devastating touch ability of a dread, using your class level to determine the total damage dealt.  This also allows you to select terrors that modify devastating touch, but these terrors only apply to the horror's use of devastating touch.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.268
Fear Surge							KEY:Fear Surge ~ Nightmare Constructor		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																		DEFINE:FearSurgeRange|30	DEFINE:FSEPhandler|0	DEFINE:FearSurgeEvolutionPoints|0	DESC:When you are within %1 ft. of a creature that suffers from the shaken, frightened, or panicked condition, you gain %2 additional evolution points to spend on the horror.  These evolution points only last while there is a creature within %1 ft. of the horror with the shaken, frightened, or panicked condition.|FearSurgeRange|FearSurgeEvolutionPoints																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														BONUS:VAR|FearSurgeEvolutionPoints|1	TEMPBONUS:PC|VAR|FSEPhandler|FearSurgeEvolutionPoints																				SOURCEPAGE:p.268
